# IOS UI Library (mandatory before any UI work)

1. READ `src/shared/LIBRARY.md` — search for an existing component or hook
2. REUSE from `@/shared/components` or `@/shared/hooks` — never duplicate UI in modules
3. EXTEND via props, `className`, or children — do not fork or copy-paste
4. NEW component only if:
   - Not in the library AND reusable in 2+ places OR clearly generic
   - Place in the correct tier folder under `src/shared/components/`
   - Add `index.ts` export and a `LIBRARY.md` entry
   - UI-only in the component file; logic in `shared/hooks/`
5. NEVER import generic UI from `@/modules/*` — only `@/shared/*`
6. Module-specific page layout stays in `src/modules/<name>/components/`

## Banned patterns (use library instead)

| Do NOT | Use instead |
|--------|-------------|
| Raw `<button>` for icon/toolbar actions | `IconButton` from `@/shared/components/ui/icon-button` |
| Inline `border-dashed` empty placeholders | `EmptyState` with `variant="dashed"` or `variant="card"` |
| Full-page centered error divs | `CenteredPageState` |
| Duplicated pill toggles | `SegmentedControl` |
| Duplicated sliding tab rows | `SlidingTabBar` |
| Inline file drop zones | `FileDropzone` |
| `feed-social-card__action-bar` markup in new code | `EngagementActionBar` kit |
